smooksCsvConfig.data: <smooks-resource-list xmlns="http://www.milyn.org/xsd/smooks-1.1.xsd" xmlns:jb="http://www.milyn.org/xsd/smooks/javabean-1.1.xsd" xmlns:csv="http://www.milyn.org/xsd/smooks/csv-1.1.xsd">   <params>     <param name="stream.filter.type">SAX</param>   </params>    <csv:reader fields="Field1,Field2,Field3,Field4" separator="," skipLines="1" />    <jb:bindings beanId="material" class="com.bokesoft.dee.mule.util.CaseInsensitiveHashMap" createOnElement="csv-record"> 	<jb:value property="name" data="csv-record/Field1"/>    <jb:value property="code" data="csv-record/Field2"/>  	<jb:value property="OWN_SHORT_NAME" data="csv-record/Field3"/> 	<jb:value property="org_code" data="csv-record/Field4"/>   </jb:bindings>    <jb:bindings beanId="ownerList" class="java.util.ArrayList" createOnElement="csv-set">     <jb:wiring beanIdRef="owner"/>   </jb:bindings> </smooks-resource-list>

smooksConfig.data: <smooks-resource-list xmlns="http://www.milyn.org/xsd/smooks-1.1.xsd" xmlns:jb="http://www.milyn.org/xsd/smooks/javabean-1.1.xsd"><jb:bindings beanId="owners" class="java.util.ArrayList" createOnElement="owners"><jb:wiring beanIdRef="owner" /></jb:bindings><jb:bindings beanId="owner" class="com.bokesoft.dee.mule.util.CaseInsensitiveHashMap" createOnElement="owner">	<jb:value property="code" data="owner/code" /><jb:value property="name"  data="owner/name" /><jb:value property="OWN_SHORT_NAME"  data="owner/shortName" /><jb:wiring property="CP_ORG_OWNER" beanIdRef="org_codes"/></jb:bindings><jb:bindings beanId="org_codes" class="java.util.ArrayList" createOnElement="org_codes"><jb:wiring beanIdRef="org_code" /></jb:bindings><jb:bindings beanId="org_code" class="com.bokesoft.dee.mule.util.CaseInsensitiveHashMap" createOnElement="org_code"><jb:value property="org_code" data="org_code/code" /></jb:bindings></smooks-resource-list>
